    "\", when translated by Facebook, becomes ‫الجسد؟\"‬ ‫لغة‬ ‫باستعمال‬ ‫نعنيه‬ ‫الذي‬ ‫.",
    "\"ما‬ Here, the phrase ‫\"باستعمال\"‬ (\"by using\") is added, subtly shifting the meaning to \"What do we mean by using body language?\"",
